## System Requirements

| Component | Requirement                         |
|-----------|-------------------------------------|
| **Python** | 3.9 - 3.12                          |
| **PyTorch** | 2.7.0 - 2.9.0                       |
| **CUDA** (optional) | 12.6 - 13.0                         |
| **C++ Compiler** | GCC 7+, Clang 5+, or MSVC 2019+     |
| **GPU** (optional) | NVIDIA with Compute Capability 6.0+ |

